<HEADLINE>
<P>
ARRESTED ENTERTAINMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Real Stories of the Highway Patrol," "Cops" and now "Top Cops." What purpose 
do these programs serve in an already violent society? Most people are aware of 
the pressures and dangers of law enforcement. It certainly is not 
entertainment. 
</P>
<P>
 Gary Traxler, Oxnard 
</P>
