<P>
BLUE OVER CARUSO 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I am deeply saddened and disappointed by the departure of David Caruso from 
"NYPD Blue" (ABC), and I don't think I'm alone in these feelings. 
</P>
<P>
 I also don't feel that Jimmy Smits can replace Caruso and I expect a drop in 
the ratings, even though Dennis Franz is staying on the program. 
</P>
<P>
 Toni Jacobson, Monterey Park 
