a report that someone smelled smoke but aides said there was no fire, just a 
short-circuit in a light fixture. 
</P>
<P>
 "A light fixture shorted out and there was a strong odor," White House press 
secretary Dee Dee Myers said. "Nothing has burned at all." 
</P>
