</P>
<P>
 The QE2 (1,814 p), a city in itself, makes regular transatlantic crossings 
between New York and Southampton, interspersed with Caribbean cruises 
throughout the year, plus a 102-day world cruise beginning Jan. 6. (800) 
221-4770. 
</P>
