 RANK: 2 
</P>
<P>
 TEAM: Nebraska (3-0) 
</P>
<P>
 SYNOPSIS: Defeated UCLA, 49-21; Quarterback Tommie Frazier's latest solid 
effort, team's 484 rushing yards proved Cornhuskers weren't guilty of looking 
past Bruins to those pesky Tigers. 
</P>
<P>
 NEXT: Pacific 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
