</P>
<P>
 SYNOPSIS: Defeated Wake Forest, 56-14; Remember Derrick Brooks? Demon Deacons 
will. After atwo-game suspension, he caused a fumble, blocked a punt and had 
five tackles and one sack. 
</P>
