to beat the Wolf Pack (2-1) of the Big West, 37-27, at Boise, Ida. . . . Micah 
Knorr kicked a 45-yard field goal and Pratt Lyons added a safety to give Utah 
State a 5-0 nonconference victory over Ohio University at Athens, Ohio. The 
Aggies (1-2) allowed the Bobcats (0-2) to cross midfield only twice, and never 
inside the 35. . . . Zoe Freeman ran for 121 yards and a touchdown and also had 
