<P>
A LITTLE BIT OF HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Cal State Northridge women's volleyball team reached the NCAA Division II 
final in 1985 for the second consecutive year but lost -- for the second 
consecutive year -- to Portland State. 
</P>
