HIGHLIGHTS 
</P>
<P>
 Ranks second on Rams' all-time reception list behind Henry Ellard (532). 
</P>
<P>
 Ranks fourth on Rams' all-time reception yardage behind Ellard (8,816), Elroy 
Hirsch (6,289) and Jack Snow (6,012). 
</P>
