Krueger, in 1955. The firm later became Nossaman, Waters, Krueger, Marsh & 
Riordan. Krueger was its senior partner specializing in natural resources. In 
addition to several articles for the Natural Resources Journal and various law 
journals, Krueger wrote books. On Sept. 11 in La Jolla. 
