<HEADLINE>
<P>
REALTY QUESTION REPRINTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Reprints of "The Top 50 Most Commonly Asked Questions About Southland Real 
Estate," which originally ran Sunday, June 12, are available from Times on 
Demand for $5.Order Document No. 2706. 
</P>
<P>
 For credit card orders delivered by fax, call the Times on Demand order line 
at 808-8463 and enter *8630. Follow the voice prompts and select option 1. 
Select option 3 for mail delivery. If you prefer to pay by check or do not have 
a touch-tone telephone, send a written request to: Times on Demand 
Publications, P.O. Box 60395, Los Angeles, Calif. 90060. Allow 2-3 weeks for 
delivery. 
</P>
